==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unloose
<hw>Un*loose"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To become unfastened; to lose
all connection or union.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unloosen</ent>⟦br⟧
